  "instructions": [
    "preheat bamboo steamer to 375 degrees fahrenheit.",
    "roll out puff pastry to a thickness of 1/8 inch.",
    "cut out circles of pastry using a cookie cutter or the rim of a glass.",
    "place a small spoonful of whipped cream in the center of each pastry circle.",
    "top with a few edible flowers and a sprinkle of powdered sugar.",
    "drizzle tempered chocolate over the top of the pastry.",
    "place the pastry in the bamboo steamer and cook for 15 minutes, or until golden brown.",
    "allow the pastry to cool slightly before serving."
